INTRODUCTION

SGGC implements a "mark and sweep" garbage collector, modified to use
several "generations", so that a complete mark and sweep is done only
occassionally.


HANDLING OLD-TO-NEW REFERENCES

Actions to do for old-to-new references when collecting at each level.

level 0:

    gen    gen
   from     to      keep?  stop?  look?

      2      0       yes     no    yes
      2      1       yes     no     no (won't anyway)
      2      2        no     no     no (won't anyway)

      1      0        no     no    yes
      1      1        no     no     no (won't anyway)
      1      2        no     no     no (won't anyway)

level 1:

    gen    gen
   from     to      keep?  stop?  look?

      2      0       yes     no    yes
      2      1        no     no    yes
      2      2        no     no     no (won't anyway)

      1      0       yes    yes     no
      1      1        no     no     no
      1      2        no     no     no (won't anyway)

level 2:

    gen    gen
   from     to      keep?  stop?  look?

      2      0       yes     no     no
      2      1        no     no     no
      2      2        no     no     no

      1      0       yes    yes     no
      1      1        no     no     no
      1      2        no     no     no
